1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,000
Imagine a bay lighting up like a starry night sky.

2
00:00:04,000 --> 00:00:08,000
This incredible display is caused by tiny organisms called dinoflagellates.

3
00:00:08,000 --> 00:00:13,200
When disturbed, they produce a brilliant blue light, creating a living light show.

4
00:00:13,200 --> 00:00:18,000
This phenomenon is most famous in places like Mosquito Bay in Vieques.

5
00:00:18,000 --> 00:00:22,000
But remember, these ecosystems are fragile and need our protection.

6
00:00:22,000 --> 00:00:24,800
Want to learn more about our oceans?

7
00:00:24,800 --> 00:00:27,600
Follow for more insights on marine life!
